        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Your slime assails the olfactory receptors. Non-osharu creatures that begin their turn adjacent to any square affected by @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.ancestry-features.Item.Slime Squirt] or @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.feats.Item.Slime Spray] must attempt a @Check[fortitude|against:class-spell] save against the higher of your class DC or spell DC. On a failure, they become @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 1} (@UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 2} on a critical failure).</p>"
